課程教材 Course Material
	     
Papers from major academic financial journals
Case Studies in Finance by Bruner, McGraw-Hill, 7th ed., 2012
Cases from Taiwan Management Case Center
Articles from Harvard Business Review and Journal of Applied Corporate Finance

     

